==Hindi==
===Etymology===
From Persian {{FAchar|[[هند]]}} ('''hend''' = ''Hindu'') +  {{FAchar|[[ستان]]}} ('''stan''' = ''land'') (''land of the Hindus'') + adjective suffix {{FAchar|[[ی]]}}.

===Adjective===
'''हिन्दुस्तानी'''
#of or pertaining to [[India]]
===Noun===
'''हिन्दुस्तानी'''
#a [[person]] from [[India]]
#[[Hindustani]] (''language'')
===Urdu spelling===
*{{URchar|[[ہندوستانی]]}}
